result.adr_address: 2 Soy St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 2 Soy St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Hilton Garden Inn Hong Kong Mongkok

reviews.text: Very kind, helpful staff. Clean rooms. VERY THIN WALLS. I was awakened by adjacent rooms every night of my stay. I could hear snoring through the wall! Even just normal conversation was easily audible. Service, great, but otherwise does not live up to Hiltom standards. Stay elsewhere.

Nice hotel in a very handy location. Good size room for Hong Kong and the staff are always happy to help as much as they can.
Bed was a little on the firm side and I like it firm so it could be said that it's very firm. 
I was there early summer so room felt a little damp for me but again not unusual for Hong Kong.
Being in Mong Kok close to plenty to do but just far enough away to get away from the hustle and bustle that occurs around Nathan road. Area is still busy good transport links.
Will stay again.

Excellent service during checkinand check-out. Housekeeper did a wonderful job; room was well cleaned. I left my computer and phone in the room after checked out and she got these items for me so quickly before I left the hotel. Breakfast was very good!

This hotel is located conveniently close to a lot of restaurants and bars so you won't be disappointed there. The rooms are clean with all the amenities you'd need to have a relaxing time but I did find the rooms to feel a little damp. It may have just been because of how humid and muggy it was outside as I was there in July. The hotel staff all spoke English, and we're friendly and accommodating. They also offer a delicious breakfast spread so be sure to grab a bite before you start your day!

Beautiful hotel in the heart of Mongkok. This hotel provides amazing service and great quality food. The bedrooms were nice and comfortable.  I enjoyed my stay and would recommend it to others as well.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角豉油街2號
result.name: 香港旺角希爾頓花園酒店

reviews.text: 新建的酒店👍位於舊區的著名星級酒店🏨👍👍

Lite kluven till detta hotell. Å ena sidan är personalen väldigt trevliga, men hårdvaran, alltså själva hotellet i sig självt, känns gammalt och lite mögligt. Det finns ett gym med 3 löpband och några andra maskiner, men ytan är verkligen liten. Hittills har poolen på taket varit avstängd pga risk för åskoväder, men det verkar som trevlig avkoppling när jag kikade genom fönstret. 
Frukosten är sämre än man önskar sig som Skandinav. Hade gärna sett annat bröd än formfranska och lite vanlig ost. Dock trevligt att de gör omelett på beställning (den är emellertid högst ordinär, helt utan finess). Plus för våfflor och färsk melon och jordgubbar! 
Internet funkar utan problem med det är inte särskilt snabbt: NEDLADDNING=5,58 Mbit/s, UPPLADDNING=3,21 Mbit/s, SVARSTID=261,85 ms.
För tillfället fungerar inte en av hissarna så det är lång väntan när man ska utnyttja dem.

가성비 좋고 편하게 이용하기 좋은 호텔.
하루밤  스톱오버도 좋지만 며칠 있기도 괜찮을 듯. 루트탑 수영장도 있고 무엇보다 주변에 자정 넘어서 오픈하는 로컬 맛집 들도 많고 홍콩 분위기 물씬 나는 볼 거리나 상정들 다수. 
딱 을지로 3가 4가 분위기로서 가족 단의보다는 상용 출장객이 선호할 만하며 택시는 콜해야 하나 늦게 옴. 랑햄에 지하철까지 멀지는 않음.

Very kind, helpful staff. Clean rooms. VERY THIN WALLS. I was awakened by adjacent rooms every night of my stay. I could hear snoring through the wall! Even just normal conversation was easily audible. Service, great, but otherwise does not live up to Hiltom standards. Stay elsewhere.

利用官網App訂房，會有一些驚喜折扣，也可以事先先在App上選擇房間，（一大床或是二小床），床鋪十分舒適，枕頭柔軟，窗簾遮光效果很棒，隔音效果不錯（旁邊是快速道路），只是房間門關上聲音較大易驚擾他人，房間內附上免費二瓶水和四瓶冷飲，這在夏天非常貼心😍
無敵市景頂樓泳池5-10月開放(7:00-22:00），健身房24小時，有更衣室洗手間，但是沒有淋浴設備，回房間才能冲澡，前台服務人員入房退房手續十分迅速且親切，寄存行李方便又安全😍
位於旺角地區，方便搭乘機場巴士丶地鐵和火車，附近就是著名朗豪坊購物中心，美食店家和超級市場距離不遠，算是方便平價的飯店😍
